The Corporate Council on Africa (CCA) will host its flagship Biennial U.S.-Africa Business Summit on June 13-16, 2017 in Washington, DC.&nbsp;The 2017 U.S.-Africa Business Summit will be one of the first opportunities for the U.S. and African private sector, and African governments to engage with the Trump Administration and key U.S. agency appointees. More than 50 speakers have been confirmed.&nbsp;More on CCA and the Summit